sub_title: Development Manager Southern North Sea at Nederlandse Aardolie Maatschappij
summary:
Petroleum Engineering Manager with 20+ years of international experience.  Proven record of developing staff, identifying and implementing technology innovations and driving change and business improvement to deliver value to the business and reduce costs. Positive, energetic, open and honest in approach.  Trusted and respected by team, colleagues, and customers.

Specialties: Oil & Gas Development management and consultancy. Staff coaching and development. Contract strategy, negotiations and managment. Stakeholder relations and alignment. Petrophysics.
